title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Nov 2 2021

description:
Clay and Buck break down what to look for as the election returns come in. The left goes insane over "Let's Go, Brandon." 'Did I do that?' Kaepernick goes after Carlton and Steve Urkel, claims white people like to see an ‘acceptable negro.' Leftist religious idol, Greta Thunberg says 'blah, blah, blah, f-bomb.'
